Time::Out - Easy timeouts
=========================

  use Time::Out ;

  # Time out the following code block after 5 seconds
  timeout 5 => affects {
    # do something that might take a long time...
  } ;
  if ($@){
    # timeout occured...
  }


INSTALLATION

Note: Your system must support alarm(2).

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install


